}}{{TIDTOC|embedded}} ==Overview== "ROCKET5T" and "UBIQUITI NETWORKS (C)2012" is silkscreened on the board in the FCC photos. :Appears to be AR934x + AR9280 based..
This device has two Ethernet ports. The main port (also the PoE input) is 10/100/1000. :The secondary port is 10/100 only.
Presumed 00:27:22 ('''[[Ubiquiti Networks]]''') OUI (on MAC label affixed to the FCC EUT and in the FCC QSG) :May also use a DC:9F:DB OUI (in original filing [FCC ID: SWX-RM5T])
